---
// About.astro
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__inner">
    <div class="about__left">
      <div class="section-label">The Vision</div>
      <h2 class="about__heading">Engineering Structured, System-Driven Enterprises</h2>
      <div class="about__divider"></div>

      <p class="about__text">
        VaC Global Solutions is an operations and technology transformation firm focused on building structured, system-driven enterprises.
        We design and implement integrated operating systems that bring visibility, control, and scalability across production, supply chain, and core business functions.
      </p>

      <p class="about__text">
        By combining process design, technology, and data, we enable organizations to move from dependency on individuals to reliable, performance-driven systems. 
        Our approach ensures consistent execution, improved operational efficiency, and the ability to scale with clarity and control.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: var(--color-surface-container-low);
  }

  .about__inner {
    max-width: 72rem; /* slightly tighter for better readability */
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about__left {
    max-width: 60rem; /* keeps text from stretching too wide */
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about__divider {
    width: 5rem;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about__text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>